name: Moving
overview: Children who live in hiding with superpowers, along with their parents who live with painful secrets of the past, face enormous dangers together.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: These three students try to hide their special abilities from other people, while their parents struggle to protect them from being used by other people.

tagline: We can be heroes or monsters.

episodes.name: Senior Year
episodes.overview: Ordinary high school student Bong-seok hides a secret.

episodes.name: Booyang: Family Support, Levitation
episodes.overview: Mi-hyun hides Bong-seok's superpowers, but the mysterious incidents on social media make her anxious.
The closer Bong-seok grows to Hui-soo, the more risk of exposure he draws

episodes.name: The Secret
episodes.overview: Bong-seok's secret is exposed and Hui-soo walks him home. Frank searches for his third target.

episodes.name: Recall
episodes.overview: Hui-soo assures Bong-seok that his secret is safe by revealing her own secret.

episodes.name: Bungaeman
episodes.overview: Jeon Gye-do's past is revealed. The NIS finds out information about Frank.

episodes.name: The Stranger
episodes.overview: Frank recalls his past as he eliminates his targets. After Frank's visit, Mi-hyun suppresses her son.

episodes.name: Black
episodes.overview: In 1994, Mi-hyun is ordered by Deputy Director Min Yong-jun to get close to and learn about the thought process of black ops agent Kim Doo-sik.

episodes.name: Humanists
episodes.overview: Doo-sik and Mi-hyun grow closer, and Doo-sik suggests that they deceive Min Yong-jun.

guest_stars.character: Director of North Korea Information Office
guest_stars.name: Park Ok-chul

episodes.name: The Monster
episodes.overview: Ju-won, who leads his gang with his monstrous abilities, is betrayed and becomes a fugitive.

episodes.name: Romanticist
episodes.overview: Ji-hee gradually opens up to Ju-won.

episodes.name: Partners
episodes.overview: Doo-sik shows up at Mi-hyun's apartment with a plan to escape Deputy Director Min for good.

episodes.name: Jang Ju-won
episodes.overview: After the Black Team disbands, Ju-won is offered a mission by Deputy Director Min to revive the team.

episodes.name: The Idiot
episodes.overview: Jae-man tries to save his wife with his strength and Ju-won is sent in to subdue him.

episodes.name: N.T.D.P.
episodes.overview: Mi-hyun and Ju-won watch the auditorium video and head to Jeongwon High, while Gye-do discovers Jun-hwa.

episodes.name: The Man Between
episodes.overview: With Mi-hyun's question, Il-hwan reminisces about his past.

episodes.name: Awakening
episodes.overview: Jun-hwa attacks Hui-soo, and Bong-seok awakens his powers to save her.

episodes.name: South and North
episodes.overview: Mi-hyun asks Deok-yoon where Doo-sik is, and he tells her what happened in the North.

episodes.name: Final Battle
episodes.overview: The fight takes a new turn with the appearance of a new North Korean superbeing, Jae-seok.
